    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for anyone looking for a reliable set of wheels that still looks great on the road. Super comfy interior and runs like a dream\u2014you\u2019re going to love it! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
