    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including double VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles high lateral G-loads without fatigue. The suspension retains its original MacPherson/Multi-link geometry, providing the tactile steering response and turn-in precision characteristic of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' status, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain sharp and track-ready.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
