    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin with supple upholstery and high-functioning tech features that make every commute a pleasure. Mechanically, this car is sound; it has been strictly maintained according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, ensuring a smooth, responsive drive with a tight suspension and quiet engine. From the clear-lens headlights to the tread-rich tires, every detail has been accounted for. It is a reliable, turn-key example ready for its next chapter.",
