    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully maintained, so it\u2019s in great shape and runs like a dream! It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is just waiting for a new owner to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a good home!",
