      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver's car. Experience the visceral 8,000 RPM redline and telepathic steering rack of a true analog icon.",
